{"type":"article","id":145,"title":"下乡精准扶贫成了下乡援交？","uid":412,"topics":[6,904,220],"contents":"前两天看到空间上转的，是原po截取自微博的内容。内容大概是说，女大学生下乡<mark>支</mark>教，却遇到了各种各样的流氓行为，包括洗澡被偷窥，甚至还有被“当媳妇”的情况。<br>\n<br>\n这些现象显然不难理解，也没什么好遮遮掩掩的，毕竟农村地区，男尊女卑的落后思想根深蒂固，要改掉没那么容易。<br>\n<br>\n但是，有关部门为了完成扶贫、执教的任务，竟然有意隐瞒这一现状，使得大批的女大学毕业生在不知道风险的情况下被骗去<mark>支</mark>教或参与精准扶贫工作，等遇到了“被当媳妇”的情况时，其权益又完全得不到保障。最可恶的是，愿意为他们发出声音的文章、微博、说说，都被“精准扶贫”式的消灭了。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180707/1530958476327025.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180707/1530958476327025.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180707/1530958476327025.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180707/1530958507836401.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180707/1530958507836401.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180707/1530958507836401.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180707/1530958527440287.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180707/1530958527440287.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180707/1530958527440287.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180707/1530958545361077.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180707/1530958545361077.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180707/1530958545361077.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180707/1530958628356768.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180707/1530958628356768.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180707/1530958628356768.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"http